    <item>
      <title>美元压低日元，日元仍展现出避险吸引力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/yen-shows-glimpses-of-haven-appeal-even-as-dollar-pushes-it-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普征收新关税后，日元周一抵御了美元最严重的冲击，表明投资者仍然认为日元在动荡时期具有避风港的价值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/yen-shows-glimpses-of-haven-appeal-even-as-dollar-pushes-it-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:29:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>滞胀风险导致美国国债收益率曲线自 11 月以来最趋平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对主要贸易伙伴加征关税的举动可能导致经济陷入滞胀，美国国债收益率曲线创下 11 周以来的最大平缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/treasuries-fall-on-short-end-as-tariffs-deepen-inflation-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 01:14:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税引发通胀和经济增长担忧，金属价格暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布对中国、加拿大和墨西哥征收关税，威胁爆发可能削弱全球经济增长的贸易战，铜、铝和铁矿石领跌金属价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-03/iron-ore-drops-as-trump-tariffs-raise-global-growth-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Feb 2025 00:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元走强抵消避险需求，黄金下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对来自加拿大、墨西哥和中国的进口商品征收关税后，金价下跌，因为在全球准备应对贸易战的情况下，美元飙升超过了避险需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/gold-edges-higher-as-trump-tariffs-unsettle-global-markets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:08:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普对美国最大原油供应国征收关税，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对包括加拿大和墨西哥原油在内的一系列进口产品征收高额关税，威胁到美国消费者的成本上涨，油价随之上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 23:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
